 when you apply for admission Incoming students will receive an award letter with the tentative financial aid offer in the mail as well    Accept or reject student loans  all in Post View    Complete the Online Loan Requirements First time Federal Direct Stafford Loan borrowers will need to complete   the Entrance Counseling and   the electronic Master Promissory Note  eMPN  online at www studentloans gov  NOTE  Entrance Counseling and eMPN must be completed prior to Matriculation in order to insure that funds will be applied towards your bill promptly  Parent PLUS borrowers must apply for the loan at www studentloans gov or download an application from our homepage under forms  Notify us of any additional aid received from outside sources  Receipt of outside awards may impact VMI s award of financial aid because the combination of all financial aid and scholarships cannot exceed the student s demonstrated need If such assistance is received  VMI will revise the financial aid award  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu Virginia Military Institute   Receiving Aid  skip to content VMI VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI Menu About About Us Administrative Offices Institute Report News  Photos  Videos VMI Archives Museums VMI Museum System The VMI Museum New Market Battlefield Stonewall Jackson House For Visitors Directions   Map Employment Parents   Family Conferences Chessie Nature Trail B